definitions.definition: A type of deformed growth occurring on the skin caused by the human papillomavirus ( HPV ).
examples: A wart has appeared on my toe.

definitions.definition: Any similar growth occurring in plants or animals, such as the parotoid glands in the back of toads.
Anything unsightly or undesirable ; a blemish .
Any of the prefixes used in Hungarian notation .
